---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <Navigation label='Home' link='/' />
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <hr class="horizontal" />
        <div class="now-container">
            <h2>/Now</h2>
            <div class="now-introduction">
                <p>
                    This page was inspired by <a href="https://sive.rs/" target="_blank">Derek Sivers</a>'s article <a href="https://sive.rs/nowff" target="_blank">The /Now page movement</a> and the community that has embraced the idea of including a <a href="https://nownownow.com/" target="_blank">now page</a> on their personal websites and blogs.
                    The purpose of this page is to show what I'm focused on (in no particular order) at this point in my life and will be updated over time.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="running-5k">
                <h3>Focus 1 -  Running 5K</h3>
                <p>At 16:28 on the 09/12/2024, I decided to start running with the goal of completing the <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/live-well/exercise/get-running-with-couch-to-5k/" target="_blank">Couch To 5K</a> program in 10 weeks.
                I plan to use the remainder of this section to track my progress:</p>
