                    <tr>
                        <td class="week">Week 3</td>
                        <td>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Run 90 seconds, Walk 90 seconds, Run 3 minutes, Walk 3 minutes, Run 90 seconds, Walk 90 seconds, Run 3 minutes, Walk 3 minutes: <span class="check-mark">&#10003;</span></li>
                                <li>Run 90 seconds, Walk 90 seconds, Run 3 minutes, Walk 3 minutes, Run 90 seconds, Walk 90 seconds, Run 3 minutes, Walk 3 minutes: <span class="check-mark">&#10003;</span></li>
                                <li>Run 90 seconds, Walk 90 seconds, Run 3 minutes, Walk 3 minutes, Run 90 seconds, Walk 90 seconds, Run 3 minutes, Walk 3 minutes: <span class="check-mark">&#10003;</span></li>
                            </ol>
                        </td>
                        <td>21/12/2024 - 27/12/2024</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="week">Week 4</td>
                        <td>
                            <ol>
                                <li>Run 3 minutes, Walk 90 seconds, Run 5 minutes, Walk 2 ½ minutes, Run 5 minutes: <span class="check-mark">&#10003;</span></li>
                                <li>Run 3 minutes, Walk 90 seconds, Run 5 minutes, Walk 2 ½ minutes, Run 5 minutes: <span class="check-mark">&#10003;</span></li>
                                <li>Run 3 minutes, Walk 90 seconds, Run 5 minutes, Walk 2 ½ minutes, Run 5 minutes: <span class="check-mark">&#10003;</span></li>
                            </ol>
                        </td>
                        <td>30/12/2024 - 03/01/2025</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="week">Week 5</td>
                        <td>
