                                <li>Run 5 minutes, Walk 3 minutes, Run 5 minutes, Walk 3 minutes, Run 5 minutes: <span class="check-mark">&#10003;</span></li>
                                <li>Run 8 minutes, Walk 5 minutes, Run 8 minutes: <span class="ballot-box">&#x2610;</span></li>
                                <li>Run 20 minutes: <span class="ballot-box">&#x2610;</span></li>
                            </ol>
