                        <td colspan="100%"></td>
                    </tr>-->
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="career">
                <h3>Focus 2 - Career</h3>
                <p>
                    I'm currently at Polaris Software as a software engineer, focusing on delivering new features for the latest version of the Chronicle operational management system.
                    <ul>
                        <li>I'm concentrating on developing my skills as a software engineer and progressing towards the next stage of my career.</li>
                    </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="home-office">
                <h3>Focus 3 - Home Office &#38; Equipment</h3>
                <p>
                    I recently purchased a standing desk with the aim of improving my posture and back health. 
                    My final aim is to stand for 15/20 minutes for every hour I spend at my desk. Currently, I stand for 5/10 minutes when at my desk. 
                    Another outcome I am considering trying out is the <a href="https://flexispot.co.uk/blog/the-20-8-2-rule-a-simple-strategy-to-avoid-the-negative-effects-of-sitting?srsltid=AfmBOoprPB05XgRPF3LklmnFtHcfyuWnASTRr7vC-tzl7WOAb1lnDlR1" target="_blank">20-8-2</a> rule.
                </p>
                <p class="aspects">Other aspects and preferences of my office/setup:</p>
                <div class="equipment-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Personal Laptop - Dell XPS 15 (9570)</li>
                        <li>Personal Desktop - custom build PC with:
                            <ul>
                                <li>Intel i7-12700K</li>
                                <li>32GB RAM</li>
                                <li>NVIDIA RTX 3060</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Phone - iPhone 13 128GB</li>
                        <li>Headphones/Earbuds:
                            <ul>
                                <li>Jabra Elite 8 Active</li>
                                <li>Anker Soundcore Space One</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
